docs {
  # Get Appointments (Schedule)
  
  Retrieves appointments with optional filtering and pagination.
  
  ## Query Parameters
  - `page`: Page number (default: 1)
  - `limit`: Items per page (default: 10)
  - `status`: Filter by appointment status (SCHEDULED, COMPLETED, CANCELLED)
  - `clinicianId`: Filter by clinician ID
  - `athleteId`: Filter by athlete ID
  - `caseId`: Filter by case ID
  
  ## Response
  Returns paginated list of appointments with athlete and clinician details.
}

